Package org.sibermatica.lang.mutable

Class MutableLong

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
org.sibermatica.lang.mutable.MutableLong
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MutableLong>, Mutable<Number>
public class MutableLong extends Number implements Comparable<MutableLong>, Mutable<Number>
A mutable long wrapper.

Note that as MutableLong does not extend Long, it is not treated by String.format as a Long parameter.

Since:
2.1
See Also:
Long, Serialized Form
